data.description: Beautiful, well maintained four bedroom, two bath home located in Creekside Village in Kyle, TX. The kitchen opens to the dining and large living area, perfect for entertaining. This home features beautiful wood like ceramic tile throughout the main living areas and walkways along with custom trim around all the windows in the living and dining. The primary bathroom includes a walk-in shower and a large walk-in closet. All conveniently located with easy access to I35, only minutes to shopping, Kyle downtown, HEB Plus, Target, Lowes, Seton Hospital, Costco and tons more.
